cases.content:
🛳 An ecosystem of founders who ship every week

@0xMonagotchi made v0.69 of Monagotchi beta and shipped 3 daily vlogs, created a pipeline to continue with 100 vlogs

@umbrella_fi upgraded its instant trade return model with quadratic slippage and an LP-positive balance mechanism in Umbrella Finance.

@hobba_io integrated Jupiter Lend, and Hobba now routes borrows to the best available rate across providers.

Yamata achieved a dual-signature flow, enabling Yamata to sign on behalf of users for automated liquidity matching.

@blend_money is deploying a custom non-custodial SMA factory for Blend Money and built fee-less bridging via CCTP V2.

@JigglypuffKing_ completed full production of 100/100 planned sets with zero failed sets for JK index.

Quantum wallet implemented a Netlify Functions backend including Stripe webhook and scheduled checks for Quantum wallet.

@AccountableData powered a $100M private credit vault launch as Valos went live using Accountable’s Data Verification Network.

@SiloPerpsDex laid the framework for AI automation integration (DEREK/Molt Mode) within Silo perpetual dex.

@Simulation_Wiki has BOX Devnet live, making Simulation fully playable with onchain test transactions.

@40acres_Finance shipped a yield optimizer for borrowers on 40 acres.

@investlyai launched the Investly platform for beta testing with live advisor onboarding and yield allocation flow.

@EclipticaOS launched its first Live Market Experiment, deploying $25k across markets on Ecliptica.

@Chainloveweb3 started building the MVP of a transactional marketplace with Chainstack for CHAIN[.]LOVE.

@cultverse_ai implemented an LLM-based structured evaluation system to score responses inside Cultverse.

@SelanetAI has sign-in live, bringing Selanet to 353 users and 2,650+ installs across 93 countries.

@TheKodeusLabs received 9,500 early builder registrations ahead of the Kodeus public launch.

@TrendleFi saw daily trading volume increase 5x week-over-week on Trendle after limit expansion and competition launch.

@GweiExchange shipped major architectural upgrades across the query layer, DEX adapters, search, and frontend of gwei.

@mondqwallet finalized the Exchange/Swap screen and dual QR + WalletConnect support inside Mobile Q wallet.

@dFusionAI is testing a new “Fusion Intelligence” model while migrating the dfusion ai data pipeline to faster processing.

@CheetahAi added Claude Sonnet 4.6 model support to Cheetah AI.

The vibe launched the complete user-facing product for the vibe that converts product images into creatives.

@boxtree_inc shipped a new-and-improved Chess game mode with full automation inside Boxtree.

@EmpowerTours deployed the EmpowerStudio Payments V2 contract on Monad, enabling per-action WMON payments for Empower Tours.

@memetok_app launched raffle tickets, allowing users to earn and claim tickets directly inside Memetok.

Playground resolved major login issues with proper Brevo SMTP integration in playground.

@ContentDAOapp has its Closed Beta live, with creators being approved into the running pool on Content DAO.

@clyr_network launched a structured Tenders system, formalizing mandate-based hiring on CLYR.

@OctoPeepsNFTs completed full checkout flow testing after pricing and upgrade logic overhaul for bocto.

@ThinkeeSenior filed a USPTO CIP and is launching the EchoSoul prototype and waitlist under Thinkee Life Net.

Bag app started core taxation integration as a key feature of the Bag app MVP.

@Replicatsai integrated with Virtuals ACP inside Replicats.

@sia_nfc completed a product demo of Sia.

@BOLTVR updated the Boltevm frontend with a functional audio-reactive Ezekiel’s Wheel experience.

@Effisend_ is presenting the first iteration of the Effisend application for Tokyo Dome ahead of the March 10 launch.

@memesteroid advanced the MEMESTROID rebrand to expand beyond memecoins toward broader crypto narrative discovery.

Argyu is migrating all payments to USDC within Argyu.

@AnodosFinance saw Anodos Wallet activity increase 10% week-over-week.

Pumpbucket shipped 75% of the Pumpbucket MVP and successfully tested pumpbucket creation.

@GrovioAI built 5 agents and is exploring long-form video creation with the Kink module inside Grovio.

@aigun_ai positioned AI GUN as the world’s first AI-powered exchange.

@captur_go released V1.0.3 with performance improvements and enhanced tablet responsiveness for Capture go.

@liquidsat_ofc had 2 meetings with a potential borrower and partner at Liquid sat.

@Timelock_Trade participated and won a prize at ETH Global Hackathon following Timelock’s pivot.

Axis partnered with Dflow and expanded Axis’s vision to include Prediction Market ETFs.

@AiLioncage shipped the full AiLioncage product from scratch in under a month.

Gathered and compiled by @greg0046
